'''安德斯·贝林·布雷维克'''（{{lang-no|Anders Behring Breivik}}，{{bd|1979年|2月13日|}}）<ref>[http://www.apdnews.com/news/34367.html 挪威杀人狂被奥斯陆大学录取攻读政治学] {{Wayback|url=http://www.apdnews.com/news/34367.html |date=20160304212346 }}，亚太日报，2013年9月13日</ref><ref name=mass-murder>{{cite news|last=Rayment|first=Sean|title=Modest boy who became a mass murderer|url=http://www.smh.com.au/national/modest-boy-who-became-a-mass-murderer-20110724-1hvh0.html|accessdate=25 July 2011|newspaper=Sydney Morning Herald|date=25 July 2011|archive-date=2016-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160725214551/http://www.smh.com.au/national/modest-boy-who-became-a-mass-murderer-20110724-1hvh0.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.skynews.com.au/topstories/article.aspx?id=641833&vId= |title=Norway suspect admits responsibility |publisher=Sky News |date= |accessdate=24 July 2011 |archive-date=2013-06-15 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6HO3sHNAG?url=http://www.skynews.com.au/topstories/article.aspx?id=641833 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vg.no/nyheter/innenriks/oslobomben/artikkel.php?artid=10080678|title=Slik var dramaet på Utøya|publisher=Verdens Gang|date=|accessdate=27 July 2011|archive-date=2012-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120331125640/http://www.vg.no/nyheter/innenriks/oslobomben/artikkel.php?artid=10080678|dead-url=no}}</ref>是一位[[挪威|挪威]][[極右翼|極右翼]]罪犯<ref>{{cite news|last=Dearden|first=Lizzie|date=20 April 2016|title=Anders Breivik: Right-wing extremist who killed 77 people in Norway massacre wins part of human rights case|work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|location=London, England|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/anders-breivik-right-wing-extremist-who-killed-77-in-utoya-norway-massacre-wins-lawsuit-against-a6992756.html|access-date=18 September 2021|archive-date=2016-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160420144616/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/anders-breivik-right-wing-extremist-who-killed-77-in-utoya-norway-massacre-wins-lawsuit-against-a6992756.html}}</ref>，2011年7月22日發生的[[2011年挪威爆炸和槍擊事件|2011年挪威爆炸和槍擊事件]]之行凶者<ref>{{cite web |author=Gavin Hewitt |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-14280210 |title=Norway gunman 'has accomplices' |publisher=Bbc.co.uk |date= |accessdate=2011-07-27 |archive-date=2011-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110825085253/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-14280210 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="suspect hints"/>。在此次[[恐怖活動|恐怖襲擊]]中，挪威[[奧斯陸|奧斯陸]]市中心[[挪威首相|首相]]辦公室附近的[[汽車炸彈|汽車炸彈]]被引爆，造成8人死亡，30人受傷。随后，在奥斯陆郊外[[烏托亞島|烏托亞島]]上，布雷维克持枪袭击了[[挪威工黨|挪威工黨]]青年營的參與者，造成69人死亡，66人受傷。由此，布雷维克实施了史上最嚴重的[[連環殺手|連環槍殺案]]。於2011年7月，有多個媒體來源指出，布雷維克極有可能會被發監至哈爾登監獄服刑。但是實際上，從被判決的次日（2012年8月25日）起，布雷維克就被關押在挪威的[[伊拉監獄|伊拉監獄]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nrk.no/227/dag-for-dag/slik-blir-breiviks-ila-hverdag-1.8294130 |title=Slik blir Breiviks Ila-hverdag |access-date=2013-07-25 |archive-date=2012-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121113085107/http://www.nrk.no/227/dag-for-dag/slik-blir-breiviks-ila-hverdag-1.8294130 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

從2015年8月起，奧斯陸大學開始向他透過遠端數位教學授課，布雷維克正式成為奧斯陸大學的學生，但是獄方保證不會讓他有進入校園的機會，也不會讓他接觸任何學生或是教職員工。

== 生平 ==
布雷维克出生於[[挪威|挪威]][[奧斯陸|奧斯陸]]，曾在商業學院修習商業管理，後居住在挪威东部開辦農場，從事农产品生意。報章報導布雷维克仍然單身，興趣是健身和打獵，也喜歡玩電玩，如[[魔獸世界|魔獸世界]]、[[決勝時刻：現代戰爭2|決勝時刻：現代戰爭2]]<ref>[http://news.chinatimes.com/focus/11050105/112011072400102.html 金髮魔獸起訴 最多判21年 中國時報]{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

布雷维克好研究政治社會問題，思想傾向於[[基督教恐怖主义|基督教恐怖主义]]，也是當地槍會成員，名下有两把获得注册的[[武器|武器]]，经常上网发表一些“[[極右派|極右派]]言论”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=8203 |title=疑兇布雷維克右傾兼反伊斯蘭 |publisher=[[Now新聞台|Now新聞台]] |date=2011-07-23 |accessdate=2011-07-24 |archive-date=2020-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920070934/https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=8203 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他还是瑞典新纳粹网上论坛的会员，网名Nordisk。2005年加入挪威右翼政党[[挪威进步党|挪威进步党]]，屡次在网上发表强烈的[[國家主義|国家主义]]言论，批评挪威的移民政策太过宽松，反对不同背景的人生活在一起<ref name="zxw">{{cite web|title=挪威袭击堪比"911"嫌犯疑为"基督教激进分子"|url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2011/07-24/3204910.shtml|publisher=中国新闻网|accessdate=2011-07-24|archive-date=2020-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200821054311/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2011/07-24/3204910.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

布雷維克在襲擊當天發布在網際網路的《2083——歐洲的獨立宣言》（''2083 – A European Declaration of Independence''）描述了自己的極右<ref name="jpost-islamophobia"/>[[激進|激進]]意識形態，<ref name="jpost-islamophobia">[http://www.jpost.com/International/Article.aspx?id=230762 'Norway attack suspect had anti-Muslim, pro-Israel views'] {{Wayback|url=http://www.jpost.com/International/Article.aspx?id=230762 |date=20130304142559 }} by Ben Hartman, ''[[The_Jerusalem_Post|The Jerusalem Post]]'', 24 July 2011</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nrk.no/nyheter/norge/1.7724781|title=Sendte ut ideologisk bokmanus en time før bomben|last=Kumano-Ensby|first=Anne Linn|date=23 July 2011|work=NRK News|language=Norwegian|accessdate=23 July 2011|archive-date=2012-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120309110537/http://www.nrk.no/nyheter/norge/1.7724781|dead-url=no}}</ref>該份宣言是用他的[[化名|化名]]Andrew Berwick發布的。<ref>{{cite web |author=AVKRISTINA OVERN |url=http://www.aftenposten.no/nyheter/iriks/article4184212.ece |title=Var aktiv i norsk antiislamsk organisasjon - Nyheter - Innenriks |publisher=Aftenposten.no |date= |accessdate=2011-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120104234902/http://www.aftenposten.no/nyheter/iriks/article4184212.ece |archive-date=2012-01-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="suspect wanted">{{cite news|url=http://www.forbes.com/feeds/ap/2011/07/24/general-eu-norway-explosion_8581470.html|agency=Associated Press|title=Lawyer: Norway suspect wanted a revolution|author=Bjoern Amland and Sarah Dilorenzo|date=24 July 2011|accessdate=24 July 2011|work=Forbes}}{{Dead link}}</ref>他的[[極端民族主義|極端民族主義]]宣言表露了他[[仇外|仇外]]的世界觀，並包括對[[文化保守主義|文化保守主義]]、[[右翼民粹主義|右翼民粹主義]]、反伊斯兰穆斯林文化、極右[[錫安主義|錫安主義]]以及[[Scorpions_(Serbia)|塞尔维亚副军国主义]]不同程度的支持。<ref name="jpost-islamophobia" /><ref name="Eurasia">{{cite news| url=http://www.eurasiareview.com/norway%E2%80%99s-bomber-should-leave-the-balkans-alone-oped-26072011/| title=Norway』s Bomber Should Leave The Balkans Alone| author=Balkan Insight| date=26 July 2011| newspaper=eurasiareview.com}}{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>而且支持暴力消滅[[伊斯蘭教|伊斯蘭教]]、[[文化馬克思主義|文化馬克思主義]]和[[多元文化政策|多元文化政策]]，以保持[[基督教|基督教]]歐洲。<ref name="jpost-islamophobia" /><ref>[http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/2011/07/25/ED111KENUV.DTL Norwegian Crime and Punishment] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fc%2Fa%2F2011%2F07%2F25%2FED111KENUV.DTL |date=20111220183239 }} by Debra J. Saunders, ''[[San_Francisco_Chronicle|San Francisco Chronicle]]'', 26 July 2011 ~ ''"... the anti-multiculturalism, anti-Muslim and anti-Marxist message of his 1,500-page manifesto."''</ref><ref name="at least">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/07/23/world/europe/23oslo.html|title=At Least 80 Are Dead in Norway Shooting|last=Goodman|first=J. David|date=23 July 2011|work=The New York Times|accessdate=23 July 2011|archive-date=2011-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110724004316/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/07/23/world/europe/23oslo.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

布雷維克承認了他所謂「殘暴但必要」的行為，但否認觸犯了法律。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.heraldsun.com.au/news/world/explosion-at-office-of-norwegian-tabloid-newspaper-vg/story-e6frf7lf-1226100159686 |title=Suspect mass murderer Anders Behring Breivik denies criminal responsibility |publisher=Herald Sun |date=2011-07-23 |accessdate=2011-07-27}}</ref><ref name="Haaretz1"/>布雷維克聲稱與挪威和國際性極右政治運動取得聯繫，<ref name="Craig Murray">{{cite web|url=http://www.craigmurray.org.uk/archives/2011/07/norwegian-killer-linked-to-tea-party-and-edl/|author=Craig Murray|title=Norwegian Killer Linked to Tea Party and EDL|publisher=Craig Murray|access-date=2011-07-28|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211213141/https://www.craigmurray.org.uk/archives/2011/07/norwegian-killer-linked-to-tea-party-and-edl/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="CH4, 25th July 2011">{{cite web |url=http://www.channel4.com/news/oslo-attacks-anders-behring-breivik-profile |title=CH4, 25th July 2011 |publisher=Channel4.com |date=2011-07-23 |accessdate=2011-07-27 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111201316/https://www.channel4.com/news/oslo-attacks-anders-behring-breivik-profile |dead-url=no }}</ref>而且屬於一個國際性反穆斯林網路的兩個在挪威和在別國的更多基層組織。警察與專家懷疑這些聲明，但沒能完全地駁回它們。<ref name="Haaretz1">{{cite news| url=http://www.haaretz.com/news/international/norway-massacre-suspect-appears-to-be-insane-his-lawyer-says-1.375379| title=Norway massacre suspect appears to be insane, his lawyer says| author=Reuters| date=26 July 2011| newspaper=[[Haaretz|Haaretz]]| accessdate=2011-07-28| archive-date=2011-07-27| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110727132425/http://www.haaretz.com/news/international/norway-massacre-suspect-appears-to-be-insane-his-lawyer-says-1.375379| dead-url=no}}</ref>

2011年7月25日，布雷維克被控犯有「顛覆或破壞社會基本運轉」和「致使群眾嚴重恐懼」，<ref name="Haaretz1"/>實施刑法中規定的恐怖主義行為，被暂时拘押八周，其中前四周单独关押以配合司法调查。<ref name="suspect hints">{{cite news|url= http://www.nytimes.com/2011/07/26/world/europe/26oslo.html?hp|date= 25 July 2011|work= The New York Times|title= Norway suspect hints that he did not act alone|author= Steven Erlanger and Alan Cowell|accessdate= 2011-07-28|archive-date= 2020-09-28|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200928154546/https://www.nytimes.com/2011/07/26/world/europe/26oslo.html?hp|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.domstol.no/upload/OBYR/Internett/Nyheter/Fengslingskjennelsen.pdf |title=Court ruling in Norwegian from the arraignment hearing in ''Oslo tingsret'', 25 July 2011. |format=PDF |date= |accessdate=2011-07-27 |archive-date=2012-04-27 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67EUel6ig?url=http://www.domstol.no/upload/OBYR/Internett/Nyheter/Fengslingskjennelsen.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>檢察官在考慮控告他犯有一項2008年法律內的[[危害人類罪|危害人類罪]]。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-14288941|title=Norway: Police ponder new Anders Behring Breivik charge|date=26 July 2011|publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]|accessdate=2011-07-28|archive-date=2020-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201231045113/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-14288941|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[2011年挪威爆炸和枪击事件|2011年挪威爆炸和枪击事件]]裡他承認是自己所為。然而在無死刑與沒有無期徒刑的挪威，他多只會面臨高21年的监禁<ref>{{cite web|author=李国荣 刘敏|title=挪威于特岛枪击事件制造者被控两项罪名|url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2011/07-24/3204743.shtml|publisher=中新网转新华网|accessdate=2011-07-24|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120193202/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2011/07-24/3204743.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並且關7年就可外出度周末不受監控，關14年便可獲得假釋的資格<ref>[http://www.nownews.com/2011/07/25/pda-91-2730300.htm 挪威殺手只關7年就可外出度周末　14年後可假釋]</ref>。而挪威法律規定若受刑人被認為對社會仍具有危險，刑滿後仍可以被延長監禁，每5年延長刑期1次，而形成實質的終身監禁。

布里維克自入獄後（2012年8月25日起，關押在挪威的{{translink|no|Ila fengsel og forvaringsanstalt|伊拉監獄}}）便住在一間由三間房間組成的小套房，共約10坪。他一早吃完早餐後便可以看報紙、有跑步機可以健身，甚至還可以使用電腦，但為了避免與外界溝通，書房的電腦並不能上網<ref>[http://iservice.libertytimes.com.tw/liveNews/news.php?no=627952&type=%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E 挪威殺人魔　竟住頂級監獄]{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.163.com/photoview/00AO0001/26788.html |title=揭秘挪威枪击案凶手布雷维克将关押监狱 |access-date=2012-08-26 |archive-date=2020-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200917183748/http://news.163.com/photoview/00AO0001/26788.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

挪威法庭裁定，布雷維克犯案時頭腦清醒，判處他最高的21年監禁<ref>[http://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8C%AA%E5%A8%81%E9%80%A3%E7%92%B0%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A%E6%A1%88%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E5%B8%83%E9%9B%B7%E7%B6%AD%E5%85%8B%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A21%E5%B9%B4-083800292.html 挪威連環襲擊案被告布雷維克判囚21年]</ref>。

布雷維克入獄後，認為他在獄中的待遇違反了人權。列舉出各種不滿，由日常生活上的不適到比較嚴重的問題都有。如獄方供應的奶油不夠塗滿麵包、只有[[PlayStation_2|PS2]]可以玩沒有[[PlayStation_3|PS3]]或[[PlayStation_4|PS4]]、只有涼咖啡可喝，囚室中沒有潤膚霜，同時囚室欠缺裝潢又沒有景觀令他沮喪。他還埋怨，他在押解時必須戴上的手銬太銳利，會「陷入他的手腕」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AB%8C%E7%89%A2%E6%88%BF%E8%A8%AD%E5%82%99%E5%B7%AE-%E6%8C%AA%E5%A8%81%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%BA%E9%AD%94%E5%91%8A%E7%8B%80-173504799.html |title=嫌牢房設備差 挪威殺人魔告狀 |access-date=2012-12-22 |archive-date=2020-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920022107/https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AB%8C%E7%89%A2%E6%88%BF%E8%A8%AD%E5%82%99%E5%B7%AE-%E6%8C%AA%E5%A8%81%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%BA%E9%AD%94%E5%91%8A%E7%8B%80-173504799.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

